<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.2">
<l>poṉṉarai nāṇoṭu māṇikkak kiṇkiṇi</l>
<l>taṉṉarai yāṭat taṉiccuṭṭi tāḻntāṭa</l>
<l>veṉṉarai mēlniṉ ṟiḻintuṅka ḷāyartam</l>
<l>maṉṉarai mēlkoṭṭāy cappāṇi māyava ṉēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that [your] belt of ruby bells along with a golden waist string</l>
<l>dances upon your waist while a single forehead ornament,</l>
<l>hanging low, sways [to and fro], having remained upon my waist,</l>
<l>drop down, clap cappāni upon the waist of the king of us cowherds! Māyavaṉ, clap cappāni!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
